      ** Initialization
 
     C                   MOVE      *BLANK        ReturnCode
     C                   MOVE      *BLANK        FldNamXAr
     C                   MOVE      *BLANK        MsgIDXAr
     C                   MOVE      *BLANK        MsgDtaXAr
     C                   Z-ADD     0             Idx
     C                   MOVE      'Y'           DDGRECOK
 
     C                   IF        DDGREC <> 'Y' AND
     C                             DDGREC <> 'N' AND
     C                             DDGREC <> ' '
 
     C                   MOVE      'N'           DDGRECOK
     C                   ADD       1             Idx
     C                   MOVEL     'DDGREC'      FldNamXAr(Idx)
     C                   MOVEL     'USS0124'     MsgIdXAr(Idx)
 
     C                   ELSE
     C                   EVAL      DFGREC = DDGREC
     C                   ENDIF
 
      ** RETURN
 
     C                   RETURN
 
